      "content": "it's more than just \"feelings\" though. it feels literal, like there's a sequence or a code in my dna that's meant to be read, but i can't find the right frequency to trigger it. do you know of any specific meditation methods that work on a biological or cellular level to unlock that kind of genetic data?",
